<H1>Making lasting changes</H1>

<P>To make lasting changes to the value of an environment
variable:</P>

<P><STRONG>1.</STRONG> Use your editor to open the <SAMP>.profile</SAMP>
file and add the line:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>VARNAME=<EM>value_of_variable</EM>;export VARNAME</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P><STRONG>2.</STRONG> Save the file and leave the editor.</P>

<P><STRONG>3.</STRONG> Enter the command:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>. .profile</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>This adds the new value to your working environment.</P>

